    «symbol Clarke-abc-Ţß-transformation
      «type: X»
      «description: Clarke (abc-alpha/beta) transformation»
      «library file: |.subckt Clarke-abc-Ţß-transformation a b c alpha beta\nB1 alpha 0 V=if( flag==0, 2/3 * ( 1*V(a) - 1/2*V(b) - 1/2*V(c) ) , sqrt(2/3) * ( 1*V(a) - 1/2*V(b) - 1/2*V(c) ) )\nB2 beta 0 V=if( flag==0, 2/3 * ( 0*V(a) + sqrt(3)/2*V(b) - sqrt(3)/2*V(c) ) , sqrt(2/3) * ( 0*V(a) + sqrt(3)/2*V(b) - sqrt(3)/2*V(c) ) )\n.ends Clarke-abc-Ţß-transformation»
      «shorted pins: false»
      «line (-300,-400) (300,400) 0 0 0x1000000 -1 -1»
